var book = {
	"name": "Joel",
	"numChapters": 3,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that came<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22293A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22293A\"></sup> to Joel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22293B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22293B\"></sup> son of Pethuel.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Hear this,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22294C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22294C\"></sup> you elders;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22294D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22294D\"></sup>listen, all who live in the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22294E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22294E\"></sup>Has anything like this ever happened in your daysor in the days of your ancestors?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22294F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22294F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Tell it to your children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22295G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22295G\"></sup>and let your children tell it to their children,and their children to the next generation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22295H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22295H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>What the locust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22296I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22296I\"></sup> swarm has leftthe great locusts have eaten;what the great locusts have leftthe young locusts have eaten;what the young locusts have left<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22296J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22296J\"></sup>other locusts have eaten.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22296K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22296K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Wake up, you drunkards, and weep!Wail, all you drinkers of wine;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22297L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22297L\"></sup>wail because of the new wine,for it has been snatched<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22297M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22297M\"></sup> from your lips.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>A nation has invaded my land,a mighty army without number;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22298N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22298N\"></sup>it has the teeth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22298O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22298O\"></sup> of a lion,the fangs of a lioness.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>It has laid waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22299P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22299P\"></sup> my vinesand ruined my fig trees.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22299Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22299Q\"></sup>It has stripped off their barkand thrown it away,leaving their branches white.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Mourn like a virgin in sackcloth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22300R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22300R\"></sup>grieving for the betrothed of her youth.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Grain offerings and drink offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22301S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22301S\"></sup>are cut off from the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.The priests are in mourning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22301T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22301T\"></sup>those who minister before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The fields are ruined,the ground is dried up;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22302U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22302U\"></sup>the grain is destroyed,the new wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22302V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22302V\"></sup> is dried up,the olive oil fails.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22302W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22302W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Despair, you farmers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22303X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22303X\"></sup>wail, you vine growers;grieve for the wheat and the barley,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22303Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22303Y\"></sup>because the harvest of the field is destroyed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22303Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22303Z\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The vine is dried upand the fig tree is withered;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22304AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22304AA\"></sup>the pomegranate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22304AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22304AB\"></sup> the palm and the apple tree—all the trees of the field—are dried up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22304AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22304AC\"></sup>Surely the people’s joyis withered away.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Put on sackcloth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22305AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22305AD\"></sup> you priests, and mourn;wail, you who minister<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22305AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22305AE\"></sup> before the altar.Come, spend the night in sackcloth,you who minister before my God;for the grain offerings and drink offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22305AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22305AF\"></sup>are withheld from the house of your God.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Declare a holy fast;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22306AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22306AG\"></sup>call a sacred assembly.Summon the eldersand all who live in the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22306AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22306AH\"></sup>to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,and cry out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22306AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22306AI\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22306AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22306AJ\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Alas for that<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22307AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22307AK\"></sup> day!For the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22307AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22307AL\"></sup> is near;it will come like destruction from the Almighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22307AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22307AM\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Has not the food been cut off<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22308AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22308AN\"></sup>before our very eyes—joy and gladness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22308AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22308AO\"></sup>from the house of our God?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22308AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22308AP\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The seeds are shriveledbeneath the clods.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22309AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22309AQ\"></sup>The storehouses are in ruins,the granaries have been broken down,for the grain has dried up.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>How the cattle moan!The herds mill aboutbecause they have no pasture;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22310AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22310AR\"></sup>even the flocks of sheep are suffering.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22310AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22310AS\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>To you, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, I call,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22311AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22311AT\"></sup>for fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22311AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22311AU\"></sup> has devoured the pastures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22311AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22311AV\"></sup> in the wildernessand flames have burned up all the trees of the field.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Even the wild animals pant for you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22312AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22312AW\"></sup>the streams of water have dried up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22312AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22312AX\"></sup>and fire has devoured the pastures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22312AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22312AY\"></sup> in the wilderness."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Blow the trumpet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22313A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22313A\"></sup> in Zion;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22313B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22313B\"></sup>sound the alarm on my holy hill.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22313C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22313C\"></sup>Let all who live in the land tremble,for the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22313D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22313D\"></sup> is coming.It is close at hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22313E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22313E\"></sup>—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>a day of darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22314F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22314F\"></sup> and gloom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22314G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22314G\"></sup>a day of clouds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22314H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22314H\"></sup> and blackness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22314I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22314I\"></sup>Like dawn spreading across the mountainsa large and mighty army<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22314J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22314J\"></sup> comes,such as never was in ancient times<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22314K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22314K\"></sup>nor ever will be in ages to come.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Before them fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22315L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22315L\"></sup> devours,behind them a flame blazes.Before them the land is like the garden of Eden,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22315M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22315M\"></sup>behind them, a desert waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22315N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22315N\"></sup>—nothing escapes them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They have the appearance of horses;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22316O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22316O\"></sup>they gallop along like cavalry.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>With a noise like that of chariots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22317P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22317P\"></sup>they leap over the mountaintops,like a crackling fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22317Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22317Q\"></sup> consuming stubble,like a mighty army drawn up for battle.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>At the sight of them, nations are in anguish;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22318R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22318R\"></sup>every face turns pale.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22318S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22318S\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They charge like warriors;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22319T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22319T\"></sup>they scale walls like soldiers.They all march in line,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22319U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22319U\"></sup>not swerving<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22319V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22319V\"></sup> from their course.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They do not jostle each other;each marches straight ahead.They plunge through defenseswithout breaking ranks.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They rush upon the city;they run along the wall.They climb into the houses;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22321W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22321W\"></sup>like thieves they enter through the windows.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22321X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22321X\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Before them the earth shakes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22322Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22322Y\"></sup>the heavens tremble,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22322Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22322Z\"></sup>the sun and moon are darkened,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22322AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22322AA\"></sup>and the stars no longer shine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22322AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22322AB\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22323AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22323AC\"></sup> thunders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22323AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22323AD\"></sup>at the head of his army;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22323AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22323AE\"></sup>his forces are beyond number,and mighty is the army that obeys his command.The day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is great;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22323AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22323AF\"></sup>it is dreadful.Who can endure it?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22323AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22323AG\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Even now,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22324AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22324AH\"></sup> to me with all your heart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22324AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22324AI\"></sup>with fasting and weeping and mourning.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Rend your heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22325AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22325AJ\"></sup>and not your garments.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22325AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22325AK\"></sup>Return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22325AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22325AL\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,for he is gracious and compassionate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22325AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22325AM\"></sup>slow to anger and abounding in love,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22325AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22325AN\"></sup>and he relents from sending calamity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22325AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22325AO\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Who knows? He may turn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22326AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22326AP\"></sup> and relent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22326AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22326AQ\"></sup>and leave behind a blessing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22326AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22326AR\"></sup>—grain offerings and drink offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22326AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22326AS\"></sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Blow the trumpet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22327AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22327AT\"></sup> in Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22327AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22327AU\"></sup>declare a holy fast,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22327AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22327AV\"></sup>call a sacred assembly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22327AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22327AW\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Gather the people,consecrate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22328AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22328AX\"></sup> the assembly;bring together the elders,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22328AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22328AY\"></sup>gather the children,those nursing at the breast.Let the bridegroom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22328AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22328AZ\"></sup> leave his roomand the bride her chamber.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Let the priests, who minister<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22329BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22329BA\"></sup> before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,weep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22329BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22329BB\"></sup> between the portico and the altar.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22329BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22329BC\"></sup>Let them say, “Spare your people, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.Do not make your inheritance an object of scorn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22329BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22329BD\"></sup>a byword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22329BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22329BE\"></sup> among the nations.Why should they say among the peoples,‘Where is their God?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22329BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22329BF\"></sup>’”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was jealous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22330BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22330BG\"></sup> for his landand took pity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22330BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22330BH\"></sup> on his people.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> replied to them:“I am sending you grain, new wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22331BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22331BI\"></sup> and olive oil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22331BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22331BJ\"></sup>enough to satisfy you fully;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22331BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22331BK\"></sup>never again will I make youan object of scorn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22331BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22331BL\"></sup> to the nations.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“I will drive the northern horde<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22332BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22332BM\"></sup> far from you,pushing it into a parched and barren land;its eastern ranks will drown in the Dead Seaand its western ranks in the Mediterranean Sea.And its stench<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22332BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22332BN\"></sup> will go up;its smell will rise.”Surely he has done great things!",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Do not be afraid,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22333BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22333BO\"></sup> land of Judah;be glad and rejoice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22333BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22333BP\"></sup>Surely the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has done great things!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22333BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22333BQ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Do not be afraid, you wild animals,for the pastures in the wilderness are becoming green.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22334BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22334BR\"></sup>The trees are bearing their fruit;the fig tree<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22334BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22334BS\"></sup> and the vine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22334BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22334BT\"></sup> yield their riches.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22334BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22334BU\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Be glad, people of Zion,rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22335BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22335BV\"></sup> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,for he has given you the autumn rainsbecause he is faithful.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22335BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22335BW\"></sup>He sends you abundant showers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22335BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22335BX\"></sup>both autumn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22335BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22335BY\"></sup> and spring rains,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22335BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22335BZ\"></sup> as before.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The threshing floors will be filled with grain;the vats will overflow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22336CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22336CA\"></sup> with new wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22336CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22336CB\"></sup> and oil.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“I will repay you for the years the locusts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22337CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22337CC\"></sup> have eaten<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22337CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22337CD\"></sup>—the great locust and the young locust,the other locusts and the locust swarm—my great army<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22337CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22337CE\"></sup> that I sent among you.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>You will have plenty to eat, until you are full,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22338CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22338CF\"></sup>and you will praise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22338CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22338CG\"></sup> the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,who has worked wonders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22338CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22338CH\"></sup> for you;never again will my people be shamed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22338CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22338CI\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then you will know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22339CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22339CJ\"></sup> that I am in Israel,that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22339CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22339CK\"></sup> your God,and that there is no other;never again will my people be shamed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22339CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22339CL\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“And afterward,I will pour out my Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22340CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22340CM\"></sup> on all people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22340CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22340CN\"></sup>Your sons and daughters will prophesy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22340CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22340CO\"></sup>your old men will dream dreams,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22340CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22340CP\"></sup>your young men will see visions.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Even on my servants,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22341CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22341CQ\"></sup> both men and women,I will pour out my Spirit in those days.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22341CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22341CR\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>I will show wonders in the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22342CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22342CS\"></sup>and on the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22342CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22342CT\"></sup>blood and fire and billows of smoke.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The sun will be turned to darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22343CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22343CU\"></sup>and the moon to bloodbefore the coming of the great and dreadful day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22343CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22343CV\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And everyone who callson the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22344CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22344CW\"></sup> will be saved;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22344CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22344CX\"></sup>for on Mount Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22344CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22344CY\"></sup> and in Jerusalemthere will be deliverance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22344CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22344CZ\"></sup>as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has said,even among the survivors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22344DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22344DA\"></sup>whom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> calls.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22344DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22344DB\"></sup>"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>“In those days and at that time,when I restore the fortunes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22345A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22345A\"></sup> of Judah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22345B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22345B\"></sup> and Jerusalem,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I will gather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22346C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22346C\"></sup> all nationsand bring them down to the Valley of Jehoshaphat.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22346D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22346D\"></sup>There I will put them on trial<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22346E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22346E\"></sup>for what they did to my inheritance, my people Israel,because they scattered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22346F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22346F\"></sup> my people among the nationsand divided up my land.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They cast lots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22347G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22347G\"></sup> for my peopleand traded boys for prostitutes;they sold girls for wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22347H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22347H\"></sup> to drink.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Now what have you against me, Tyre and Sidon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22348I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22348I\"></sup> and all you regions of Philistia?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22348J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22348J\"></sup> Are you repaying me for something I have done? If you are paying me back, I will swiftly and speedily return on your own heads what you have done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22348K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22348K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For you took my silver and my gold and carried off my finest treasures to your temples.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22349L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22349L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You sold the people of Judah and Jerusalem to the Greeks,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22350M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22350M\"></sup> that you might send them far from their homeland.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“See, I am going to rouse them out of the places to which you sold them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22351N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22351N\"></sup> and I will return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22351O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22351O\"></sup> on your own heads what you have done.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will sell your sons<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22352P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22352P\"></sup> and daughters to the people of Judah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22352Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22352Q\"></sup> and they will sell them to the Sabeans,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22352R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22352R\"></sup> a nation far away.” The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22352S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22352S\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Proclaim this among the nations:Prepare for war!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22353T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22353T\"></sup>Rouse the warriors!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22353U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22353U\"></sup>Let all the fighting men draw near and attack.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Beat your plowshares into swordsand your pruning hooks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22354V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22354V\"></sup> into spears.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22354W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22354W\"></sup>Let the weakling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22354X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22354X\"></sup> say,“I am strong!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22354Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22354Y\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Come quickly, all you nations from every side,and assemble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22355Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22355Z\"></sup> there.Bring down your warriors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22355AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22355AA\"></sup> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Let the nations be roused;let them advance into the Valley of Jehoshaphat,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22356AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22356AB\"></sup>for there I will sitto judge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22356AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22356AC\"></sup> all the nations on every side.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Swing the sickle,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22357AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22357AD\"></sup>for the harvest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22357AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22357AE\"></sup> is ripe.Come, trample the grapes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22357AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22357AF\"></sup>for the winepress<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22357AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22357AG\"></sup> is fulland the vats overflow—so great is their wickedness!”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Multitudes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22358AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22358AH\"></sup> multitudesin the valley<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22358AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22358AI\"></sup> of decision!For the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22358AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22358AJ\"></sup> is nearin the valley of decision.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22358AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22358AK\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The sun and moon will be darkened,and the stars no longer shine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22359AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22359AL\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will roar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22360AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22360AM\"></sup> from Zionand thunder from Jerusalem;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22360AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22360AN\"></sup>the earth and the heavens will tremble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22360AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22360AO\"></sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be a refuge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22360AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22360AP\"></sup> for his people,a stronghold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22360AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22360AQ\"></sup> for the people of Israel.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Then you will know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22361AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22361AR\"></sup> that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22361AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22361AS\"></sup>dwell in Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22361AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22361AT\"></sup> my holy hill.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22361AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22361AU\"></sup>Jerusalem will be holy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22361AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22361AV\"></sup>never again will foreigners invade her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22361AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22361AW\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“In that day the mountains will drip new wine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22362AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22362AX\"></sup>and the hills will flow with milk;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22362AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22362AY\"></sup>all the ravines of Judah will run with water.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22362AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22362AZ\"></sup>A fountain will flow out of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s house<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22362BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22362BA\"></sup>and will water the valley of acacias.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22362BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22362BB\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22363BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22363BC\"></sup> will be desolate,Edom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22363BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22363BD\"></sup> a desert waste,because of violence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22363BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22363BE\"></sup> done to the people of Judah,in whose land they shed innocent blood.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Judah will be inhabited forever<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22364BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22364BF\"></sup>and Jerusalem through all generations.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Shall I leave their innocent blood unavenged?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22365BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22365BG\"></sup>No, I will not.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22365BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22365BH\"></sup>”The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> dwells in Zion!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22365BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22365BI\"></sup>"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;